      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit features the M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for crisp, sub-100ms shifts and is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) for adjustable chassis response. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, ensuring the structural integrity of the valvetrain and bottom end. The M Variable Differential Lock remains tight, providing exceptional lateral grip. A driver-focused example that prioritizes peak performance and engine harmonics.",
