      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 BMW M3 finished in timeless Alpine White. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and exhilarating daily driver. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and hood, as expected from regular road use. The 19-inch alloy wheels are in great shape with no major curb rash. Inside, the cabin features premium Black Merino leather that has been kept clean and conditioned; there is some light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the interior remains smoke-free and smells fresh. All technological features, including the iDrive system, heads-up display, and heated seats, are fully operational. Under the hood, the twin-turbo inline-six runs flawlessly. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule with oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the car recently received a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires and a brake fluid flush. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the perfect balance of performance and practicality for its next owner.",
